aboutpara: An innovative and analytical thinker with a strong passion for software development, eager to expand my knowledge and skills. I have been actively enhancing my software development expertise through my education at Northcoders and practice exercises on FreeCodeCamp. Coding is not just a skill but a genuine interest of mine, as evidenced by my personal projects, including the development of an app and a Firefox extension aimed at enhancing reading accessibility for individuals with ADHD. I am deeply committed to continuous learning and am enthusiastic about the opportunity to contribute as a Junior Software Developer.
